    "Use 'Built in the glass' and 'served up' to calculate the ABV of your own batches. Those two combined will not add any dilution to the drink.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Verwenden Sie „Im Glas eingebaut“ und „serviert“, um den Alkoholgehalt Ihrer eigenen Chargen zu berechnen. Beides zusammen führt zu keiner Verdünnung des Getränks."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Use 'Built in the glass' and 'served up' to calculate the ABV of your own batches. Those two combined will not add any dilution to the drink."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Utilisez «Construit dans le verre» et «Servi» pour calculer l'ABV de vos propres lots. Ces deux combinés n’ajouteront aucune dilution à la boisson."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Usa 'Costruito nel bicchiere' e 'servito' per calcolare il grado alcolico dei tuoi lotti. Questi due combinati non aggiungeranno alcuna diluizione alla bevanda."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Usa 'Construido en el vaso' y 'servido' para calcular el ABV de tus propios lotes. Esos dos combinados no añadirán ninguna dilución a la bebida."
          }
        }
      }
    },
